      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs silently, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
