      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This car is ready to go! It's in honest, fair condition, meaning it has some expected wear and tear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid and dependable choice for your commuting needs. It\u2019s a functional, budget-friendly option for someone who values performance over a perfect exterior. Come see its character for yourself!",
